yatra tu tādṛśaḥ prakarṣo nāsti tatra kulāntaravyapadeśanibandhanābhāvātsattvakulenaiva vyapadeśaḥ | saṃkṣepeṇa tu pañcadheti sattvakulasya tattatkulānukāriṇastatra tatra saṅgrahāt | traividhye 'pyevameva |

<commentary>kāni punastānyādibhūtāni kulāni yatkulānyaparāṇi bhaviṣyanti | kathaṃ ca tāni kulamityucyanta ityāha—kulānāmityādi |
pañca bhūtāni skandhā vā kulāni tadviśuddhirūpatvādeva buddhānām | tadrūpatvena vajradharasya | teṣāṃ ca tadanantaramaparimitena rūpeṇa | yattveṣāṃ kulamityabhidhīyate tattadrūpeṇa | pañca bhūtāni pṛthivyāptejovāyuvijñānāni | pañca skandhā rūpavedanāsaṃjñāsaṃskāra |</commentary>

nanvevaṃ śūnyatā tattvam | mudrāyogājjapanāccopāyopetaṃ tadupasūcitam | na tviha kiñcidbhāvyamupadiṣṭamutpannarūpāṇāmeva pañcakulānāṃ yoginīnāṃ nirdeśādyogināṃ ca taddvāreṇaiva tathā sūcanāt |